title: Beautifully updated kitchen. Dishwasher-  Hardwood Floors VIDEO TOUR!
posting_body: ['1939 Bryant Ave S- Sits between Lyndale and Hennepin Ave S.', 'Walking distance to so many great fun restaurants, bars and shops of Uptown', "Close to The Wedge, Sebastian Joe's, and Mortimer's", 'Available September 1', 'Newly Remodeled and GORGEOUS!', 'Updated Kitchen- Gas Range Stove', 'DISHWASHER', 'Refinished hardwood floors', 'Original, gleaming woodwork', 'Dog friendly', 'Dining room and open living room', 'Check out the video tour!', 'https://youtu.be/5lSWmrseqsM', 'The video is the exact unit and the photos are staged but the kitchen is the correct one as well.', '$1,295 includes your heat, water, trash, and recycling;', 'Tenants pay cooking gas, electricity, and optional cable/internet', 'Deposit: $1,295', 'Application fee: $40 per person', 'Dog Deposit: $300', 'Dog Rent is $40 a month and we do have some dog restrictions- check out <URL> for details', 'Sorry no other pets allowed', 'Parking available for $65/mo', 'Please be sure to check out application on line and qualifications and requirements', '<URL>', 'Give IrvingProperties a call or email', 'show contact info', 'to set up a showing.', 'Locally owned and professionally managed!']
